ConstValues.value: "console.log('Setting window.close');var _close = window.close; window.close= function(){if(window['webkit'] && window['webkit'].messageHandlers.mluviiLibrary) { window['webkit'].messageHandlers.mluviiLibrary.postMessage({type:'close', value: 'true'}) } };var mluviiEventHandler = function(event,sessionId){if(window['webkit'] && window['webkit'].messageHandlers.mluviiLibrary){ window['webkit'].messageHandlers.mluviiLibrary.postMessage({type:'sessionEnded', value: [event,sessionId]}); }}; window.mluviiEventHandler = mluviiEventHandler;"
